text: Woytkowskia gruberi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 1992. It is known from Costa Rica.BioLib.cz - Woytkowskia gruberi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1992
title: Woytkowskia gruberi
